headline: Baron Health Care Fund Reacquired Edwards Lifesciences Corporation (EW) in Q2. Here’s Why
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Health Care Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
